{"tid":1491974,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚被斬傷既記者個好朋友有野想講","createTime":"2019-08-20T15:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T18:20:11.000Z","uid":58785,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"86f77b78dae98fa24f38357073716e89972d6aab","tid":1491974,"uid":58785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/98LFvUx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F98LFvUx.png&h=c76a6b6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/chantt.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fchantt.hk%2F&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9kzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=0a71754f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/chantt.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n陳壇丹係邊個？佢同受傷個女仔係同一屆既莊員<br />\n同時 佢係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民建聯</span></strong></span>既社區主任<br />\n浸大英文系grad 仲去過佔中 教左幾年書之後為左從政放棄教書走左去民建聯度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以留意下面d comment 基本上圍屌佢既全部都係佢d下莊<br />\n口口聲聲話關心自己個好朋友 但被人踢爆佢由六月開始就深潛冇覆過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前排佢叫人去守護香港集會仲俾佢以前上莊個soc出埋聲明割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3645f1d1ed69c0357ee4827c50453bff76ec63c","tid":1491974,"uid":203417,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:36:38.000Z","msg":"靚唔靚㗎？"},{"pid":"98f6681a3c636b4f29759feb19919230cba383f1","tid":1491974,"uid":58785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3645f1d1ed69c0357ee4827c50453bff76ec63c","tid":1491974,"uid":203417,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:36:38.000Z","msg":"靚唔靚㗎？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:37:19.000Z","msg":"男人黎架屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1cdbfba575fcdc22fba0